{"tid":1815801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港獨立是唯一出路","createTime":"2020-01-07T19:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T19:47:47.000Z","uid":337052,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0867703a8b7dd49424ad99b7c27f8a47131fcf2","tid":1815801,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:28:38.000Z","msg":"香港獨立是唯一出路<br />\n<br />\n為什麼台灣強制被叫作中華台北，不是叫台灣嗎?<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n台灣獨立運動（臺灣話：T&acirc;i u&acirc;n to̍k li̍p ūn tōng），簡稱台獨（T&acirc;i to̍k），是台灣獨派的核心政治理想及國家認同，其主張解除1949年後才遷台的國民政府之政權、質疑其治台正當性及制定新憲法並將國號－「中華民國」更名為「台灣」（Taiwan）等之稱呼，建立一個屬於全體台灣人的主權國家[1]，與謀求兩岸統一的「統派」相對。實際上依照理論與目標的不同，還可細分為傳統台獨派及台獨左派等流派；但與「華獨」流派概念不同的是，華獨主張「中華民國是台灣」，認為現時台澎金馬自由地區已經「事實獨立」（de facto）已是主權獨立國家。<br />\n<br />\n台灣獨立運動面臨著種種的政治現實與國際角力，外部除須與美、日兩大國家建立互信的「美日台安保條約」[2]，還須克服來自中華人民共和國的武力干涉[3]與經濟施壓[4]，而如何解決台灣內部在國家認同與意識形態上的多元與矛盾（統派、華獨人士）也是另一項難題[5][6]。台灣獨立運動也透過台灣民族主義、台灣本土化運動[7]、台灣正名運動[8]、去中國化[9]、強調台灣主體性等方式表現。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=35f45349\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣獨立團體有很多<br />\n台灣基進黨<br />\n<a href=\"https://statebuilding.tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatebuilding.tw%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=da4e5aee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://statebuilding.tw/</a><br />\nFAPA<br />\n<a href=\"https://fapa.org/wp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffapa.org%2Fwp%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=e9294683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fapa.org/wp/</a><br />\n鯨魚網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hi-on.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hi-on.org%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=c4c1bb8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hi-on.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n=================================================<br />\n<br />\n香港正在經歷台灣的戒嚴時期<br />\n如果香港不獨立，就會成為沒有根的民族<br />\n台灣人希望可以幫香港"},{"pid":"1bd891a832e132a1350c44e32b9a7c72db13a45a","tid":1815801,"uid":338893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:30:10.000Z","msg":"想推但P牌不能評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe856016b4ac4be2dcde97651a30071c2fd35daf","tid":1815801,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:45:59.000Z","msg":"其實係人都知香港要獨立先得<br />\n<br />\n但大家都好偽善 始終被洗腦龍的傳人太多年 睇古裝劇太多年<br />\n<br />\n你睇 來個新既支聯主任 幾多人即刻話下個到林鄭 好開心咁 十足十以前古裝劇果d皇上最終明察秋毫咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五千年奴性 唔易甩"},{"pid":"2c4ece1207d582576feb1aa1c315bb5b1ca8b2df","tid":1815801,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bd891a832e132a1350c44e32b9a7c72db13a45a","tid":1815801,"uid":338893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:30:10.000Z","msg":"想推但P牌不能評分<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:53:13.000Z","msg":"謝謝"},{"pid":"2dcabe26806f5a91cc13f6c5dc47ce18d8415693","tid":1815801,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe856016b4ac4be2dcde97651a30071c2fd35daf","tid":1815801,"uid":271130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T19:45:59.000Z","msg":"其實係人都知香港要獨立